data.description: Stunning Home with Privacy, Acreage and Modern Amenities  Experience the perfect balance of privacy and convenience with this beautiful property. It features three spacious bedrooms and two completely remodeled full baths. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, with a large 10x9 en-suite and walk-in closet. You'll love the outdoor space, complete with a deck, patio, and a sprawling fire pit area that's perfect for entertaining. This just-under-4-acre property also has a 3-stall barn, a 10x20 run-in shelter, and fence – all ready for your horses to enjoy. 2023 New roof, HVAC, Drywall, floor, updated kitchen and bathrooms.
